title: 21 Secret Remedies for Colds and Flu
description:
21 Secret Remedies for Colds and Flu: Build Your Immune System and Stay Healthy--Naturally! 
English | ISBN: 1629980102 | 2015 | 128 pages | EPUB | 1 MB

A healthy immune system is the key to winning the battle over the flu and other illnesses we are faced with on a daily basis. With contributions from our most popular health authors, including Dr. Leslie Ann Dauphin of the CDC, Dr. Don Colbert, Janet Macarro, Cherie Calbom, and more, this book gives you natural, practical ways to build your immune system and stay healthy during the cold and flu season. With biblical perspectives, the latest scientific research on alternative health practices, and expert advice from the Centers for Disease Control and Prevention professionals, doctors, nutritionists, and naturopathic practitioners
